{"tid":881727,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★生活只剩工作　31歲藝術家患驚恐症　靠運動減壓","createTime":"2018-10-29T16:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T03:17:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7282e7afb0a9bc79d3743b722bc749c72fa57621","tid":881727,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2028474/org/2eadc265cb0d619340aa35b2670984b8.jpg/gtFJvkQcBAl0-CQxOIDKsOYV-MSMnYKgfNTAi3zUwIs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2028474%2Forg%2F2eadc265cb0d619340aa35b2670984b8.jpg%2FgtFJvkQcBAl0-CQxOIDKsOYV-MSMnYKgfNTAi3zUwIs&h=ce4db54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n31歲的廖家宜在中四患上思覺失調，常看到奇怪的影像和聽到怪聲。當時她正修讀藝術，便透過畫畫，把恐懼畫出來，藏在將被丟棄的報紙裡，以紓解情緒，並漸漸康復。<br />\n<br />\n減壓方式變成壓力來源<br />\n<br />\n後來，廖家宜從事藝術行業。她憶述，當時生活只剩下工作，沒有任何娛樂，亦無法與家人分享到任何生活上的事。當興趣成為工作，原本的減壓方式變成壓力，「創作不到會給自己壓力，而且自己是完美主義者，為達完美會放棄休息。」壓力太大的情況下，她開始對身邊的事失去興趣，並出現心跳加速、手震、不能呼吸、專注力下降等問題。<br />\n<br />\n她在今年年初確診驚恐症，剛好她任教的畫班中，有學生家長任職精神科護士，發現自己情緒出現問題後，便向那位家長求助，在家長的建議下求醫。<br />\n<br />\n現在，廖家宜會做運動如長跑、游泳、打羽毛球減壓。她表示，現時每星期會跑步3至4日，「長跑已很辛苦，只會想要跑到哪裡，不會想到其他煩惱。」此外，她會盡量控制作息時間，如下午7時後便盡量不回覆工作上的電郵。<br />\n<br />\n廖家宜認為，當發現自己情緒出現困擾時，不要藏在心裡，要找身邊的人傾訴，並呼籲社會不要醜化或歧視病人，「患病不是病人的錯。」<br />\n<br />\n精神科專科醫生、研究工作小組召集人麥永接建議市民應定時為自己「充電」，不要待耗盡才充，並需平衡工作與生活，或整合工作與生活，懂得放工、放假，需要時向專業人士求助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/252645/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%8F%AA%E5%89%A9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-31%E6%AD%B2%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6%E6%82%A3%E9%A9%9A%E6%81%90%E7%97%87-%E9%9D%A0%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%B8%9B%E5%A3%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F252645%2F%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%2589%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-31%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2582%25A3%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%2581%2590%25E7%2597%2587-%25E9%259D%25A0%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25A3%2593&d=DvMoTCykZC%2Fzp7oLk9hUo2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=48a30c52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/252645/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%8F%AA%E5%89%A9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-31%E6%AD%B2%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6%E6%82%A3%E9%A9%9A%E6%81%90%E7%97%87-%E9%9D%A0%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%B8%9B%E5%A3%93</a>"},{"pid":"1311a7b48b7bf9679e97018c55c0265c1afff135","tid":881727,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a723255744c8c0d42d690fcafb3a47fa80ea08","tid":881727,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:08:27.000Z","msg":"首歌幾好聽"},{"pid":"821fab8100608049ad61d1e8b7b5695a04fd9933","tid":881727,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:11:53.000Z","msg":"可以拎白卡"},{"pid":"c58f2aae2f4214e1e9eda0dfdd812ce77bf6a0eb","tid":881727,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"821fab8100608049ad61d1e8b7b5695a04fd9933","tid":881727,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:11:53.000Z","msg":"可以拎白卡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"2b11f8b6cb51b9d46195455fed4aa7082129db4b","tid":881727,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">689都係藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"}]}